AnnotationInfo.Annotation:
注：自定义邮件的附件，支持以下通配符
@AccountNo：客户账号
@AccountName：客户简称
@AccountEngName：英文简称
@FulllName：客户全称
@EngFullName：英文全称
@AccountAddress：联系地址
@CashInBankName：入金银行名称
@CashInAccount：入金账户
@RegDate：注册日期
@AuthExpireDate：授权到期日
@CurrentTradeDate：当前交易日
@LastSettleDate：上一结算日
@Date：结单日期(专用)
不勾选按客户匹配附件，则所有附件对所有客户发送

Note: Custom mail attachments support the following wildcards
@AccountNo: Customer account
@AccountName: Customer abbreviation
@AccountEngName: English abbreviation
@FulllName: Customer full abbreviation
@EngFullName: English full abbreviation
@AccountAddress: Contact address
@CashInBankName：Bank name
@CashInAccount：Bank account
@RegDate：Registered date
@AuthExpireDate：Authorized expire date
@CurrentTradeDate：Current trade date
@LastSettleDate：Last settle date
@Date：Settle bill date(Special)
If you do not check the matching by customer, all attachments will
be sent to all customers.

注：消息标题和消息内容，支持以下通配符
@AccountNo：客户账号
@AccountName：客户简称
@AccountEngName：英文简称

Note: The message header and message content support the following wildcards
@AccountNo: Customer account
@AccountName: Customer abbreviation
@AccountEngName: English abbreviation
